FT  30 APR 94 / UK Company News: Champneys health group changes hands
Champneys, the health group, has been acquired by Fitness &amp; Leisure
Holdings, a holding company which manages Inglewood Health Hydro in the UK
and a Canadian leisure development. The price is undisclosed.
Champneys Group includes Champneys at Tring, the Spa at Gleneagles and the
London Club at Le Meridien Hotel, London. Over the years it has benefited
from substantial capital improvements by both Allied Investments and
Guinness.
